                "image": {
                    "type": "image",
                    "name": "Advice and Rules",
                    "image": "Sidebar_1_AdviceAndRules.png"
                },
                "html": "Some chupacabras are mutants with large reptilian wings and have been known to carry off goats or even children. A winged chupacabra has a fly Speed of 50 feet. Other chupacabras grow much larger, up to Medium sized, and can stand eye to eye with a full-grown human. These chupacabras have <a aonid=\"790\" game-obj=\"Rules\">elite adjustments</a> to their statistics and deal 2d6+5 damage with their jaws Strikes."
            }
        ],
